node.text: Yesterday was #WorldOvershootDay - the day when we have used all the resources the earth can reasonably regenerate in a year. Artificially 3 weeks later than last year due to #COVID19. Noting also that this day would have come on 14th March for the US (and a similar date for other consumption led economies). A telling reminder that we are exploiting the world's resources unsustainably. It's no longer a theoretical date, the impacts on our lives through extreme weather and pollution are becoming ever clearer.

I know a lot of people in Melbourne are struggling with this second lockdown. I thought sharing some resources that might help people to support their people may be helpful.

If you are not sure about asking someone R U OK or you are worried what the answer will be.

The @ruokday website has some really great resources to help prepare you:
To notice the signs that it might be a good time to ask R U OK?
To help prepare you to ask R U OK?

If you need help click find help on their website for an extensive list of support services available in Australia.

If someone’s life is at risk call 000
If you need immediate support please call
LIFELINE 13 11 14
BEYOND BLUE 1300 22 4636
Suicide Call Back Service 1300 659 467
Kids Helpline 1800 55 1800

You can also get access to 20 Medicare-subsidised psychology sessions up until 31 March 2021. It then goes back to 10.
The first step of this process is to make an appointment with your GP to develop a mental health treatment plan.

Look after yourself (in what ever way that looks like for you) Melbourne friends 💖

node.text: Such a great job your doing Anna 🙏🙏🙏
Such a great job your doing Anna 🙏🙏🙏

Just a check in post for you all to let you know that we’re still continuing to send out our crisis food packs to those that are needing support across Bali. We had some information come through to us via a close Saudara friend; Putu, that a particular village near his home in the west was not doing well at all. The Balinese people are such a beautiful culture and have always had an amazing sense of community and sharing amongst them. They are incredibly selfless and will look at the wider village they live in rather than their immediate family to make sure everyone is ok. Everything is shared and they will look to make sure that everyone is ok. At the moment with money being incredible sparse and this meaning less and less available food, it’s harder for them to share. We delivered 30 food packs to this village and I’ll aim to share the stories of these people along the way so you can get a real insight as to why this food is vital and how your donations have made such a difference🙏

This is Nurah Alit and he is 21 years old. He normally works peeling coconuts for a business that sells coconuts to many restaurants and beach clubs. As these are now all closed to to bo tourism, he lost his job. He has not worked for nearly 5 months, but it’s still expected that as a young man he will continue to provide for his family. The food packs you have donated are making a huge difference in the lives of these people. Anna x💜💜☀️🌴

Не планировали такой отпуск, но когда появилась возможность, я подумала: "А почему бы и нет?"
⠀
Я никогда не была в санатории, поэтому грядущая поездка вызывала восторг и любопытство.
⠀
Санаторий находится в Новосибирске, называется @parus_resort
⠀
Отдых проходит легко и спокойно. Помимо процедур, мы очень много гуляем в парке, на свежем воздухе.
⠀
В обязательном порядке у нас дискотека для детей, куда моя дочь бежит вперёд, мне остаётся лишь не отставать😁 Также из обязательного детская площадка.
⠀
Пару раз получилось поймать теплую погоду и сходить в открытый бассейн, который навеял воспоминания об отдыхе в Турции 😊
⠀
Я не стала брать с собой ноутбук, так как здесь практически нет времени работать. Всё моё время посвящёно дочери 😊 Отпуск должен быть отпуском, даже если это санаторий.
⠀
Я чувствую, что действительно отдыхаю. Моя голова разгружается и в ней появляются новые мысли и новые идеи🙌
⠀
Понимаю, что я даже уже соскучилась по работе, но впереди ещё неделя отдыха.
⠀
А затем с 5 сентября снова начну радовать вас своими изделиями🤗

SWIPE to read the paper 👉🏼

Recent research suggesting gluthatione deficiency is a contributing factor to serious display of and consequences of COVID -19.
.
.
Initially, research thought it might be due to Vitamin D deficiency, and while that still may be true, it appears to be a secondary deficiency as a result of glutathione deficiency. (Last image) 
.
.
Glutathione is a major antioxidant and reduces oxidative stress and lowers inflammation. 
.
.
We need a strong, efficient LIVER - one that is not overloaded to make our own gluathione (“endogenous”) but we can also get glutathione from our diet (“exogenous”) in fresh fruit and vegetables.
.
.
Oh wait?! 🤚🏼🤚🏼🤚🏼
Did the simple fruit and veg just win the arguement again?! 
Hmmm 🤔 must be a staple of a healthy person’s diet. 
.
.
I think you catch my drift 🤪

.
Program musik SBS ‘Inkigayo’ akan menayangkan berbagai penampilan dari para idol lebih awal dari biasanya. .
‘Inkigayo’ sendiri normalnya ditayangkan setiap hari Minggu pada pukul 15.50 KST, sehingga penayangan dimajukan 45 menit lebih awal. Episode ‘Inkigayo’ pada minggu ini akan menayangkan berbagai penampilan dari idol mulai dari ITZY, DreamCatcher, ONEUS, MCND, DONGKIZ dan masih banyak lainnya. Seperti yang diketahui, di Korea Selatan, khususnya Seoul saat ini dalam kondisi yang serius karena meningkatnya kasus COVID-19 yang bahkan dikabarkan telah menginfeksi beberapa publik figur

node.text:
BOLETIM N° 153 - COVID-19

MONTE MOR REGISTRA MAIS QUATRO NOVOS CASOS POSITIVOS PARA COVID-19 E SOMA CHEGA A 1.126

A Prefeitura de Monte Mor, por meio do Comitê de Enfrentamento e Prevenção ao Novo Coronavírus, registrou neste sábado (22 de agosto) mais quatro casos positivos para COVID-19. Com a soma das últimas 24 horas o total de infectados desde o início da pandemia subiu para 1.126 pessoas atingidas pela pandemia.

De acordo com a Secretaria Municipal de positivos atingiram uma mulher de 39 anos do Jardim Campos Verdes, uma jovem de 17 anos do Centro, um adolescente de 17 anos do Jardim Panorama e um homem de 46 anos do Jardim Paviotti. Todos passam bem e estão em quarentena em suas respectivas residências. 

Até o momento, a Secretaria Municipal de Saúde de Monte Mor contabilizou oficialmente 3.384 exames realizados (notificações), sendo 2.247 negativos e 11 no aguardo do laudo conclusivo do exame que se encontra em análise laboratorial. Todos os 11 pacientes que aguardam resultados estão em isolamento social em suas respectivas residências. Até o momento, dos 1.126 casos positivos, 907 se encontram curados, 182 em quarentena residencial, seis seguem internados e 31 mortes confirmadas.

Meet our speaker 

@bensonuzoma 

In 2011, Benson obtained his Bachelor of Medicine, Bachelor of Surgery (MBBS) degree from the University of Nigeria Teaching Hospital (UNTH) where he received an award for contributing positively to patient care and dedication to duty in the Neurosurgical ward as a house officer. 

He has a Master’s Degree in Business Administration with distinction from the Obafemi Awolowo University.

 

He worked with Jonex Specialist Hospital, Aba, as a medical officer. Thereafter in 2013, he served as the Chief Medical Director for the Oyo State National Youth Service Corps. He was employed as a Senior Medical Officer and Administrative Assistant at J-Rapha Hospital and Maternity, Ibadan, where he acquired numerous administrative skills with commendation for improving health services and carrying out his duties passionately.

 

Subsequently, he was employed by KBL Healthcare, a national Health Maintenance Organization (HMO) as the Medical Operations Officer covering South-West Nigeria. In less than 2years he was promoted to Head, Provider Administration, overseeing the company’s medical operations, risk management and client services nationwide. Later, he was hired by Oceanic Health Management Limited, one of the biggest national HMOs in Nigeria as a regional manager.

He is a medical professional with an entrepreneurial and  sales background.

اپیدمی کرونا و لزوم فاصله گذاری اجتماعی، سیستم های آموزشی در سراسر جهان را با چالش هایی روبرو کرد.
مواجهه سیستم های آموزشی با این چالش ها، تحولات چشمگیری در آموزش ایجاد کرد طوری که دانش آموزان/دانشجویان شیوه ی کاملا متفاوتی از تحصیل را تجربه کردند.
اهمیت آموزش از راه دور بیش از پیش نمایان شد و نشان داد که آموزش در آینده به صورتی کاملا متفاوت از آنچه پیش از بروز کرونا پیش بینی می شد خواهد بود و آموزش مجازی/آنلاین بخش تفکیک نشدنی یک سیستم آموزشی نوین خواهد بود.

node.text:
Por qué las y los trabajadores de Chile tenemos que vivir en estas condiciones? El pueblo trabajador vive hace mucho en la precariedad, estas condiciones han sido las mejores para que el covid se reproduzca y afecte en mayor medida a los sectores más populares. Las y los profesionales convocacion nos comprometemos a trabajar y luchar por acabar con la desigualdad y el mercado que producen esta precariedad.

Although the #COVID19 global pandemic has drastically changed the way we operate, it has also offered us, at Sheron Ann Foundation, an unexpected opportunity to shift to a new way of connecting. It has widened our abilities to serve in ways we could not have imagined before.
Working at a distance has its difficulties, but through these struggles to stay safe and protect each other, we have gained a deeper understanding of the reach our advocacy has, and its ability to surpass any barrier it comes against. 
I want to give a special #ThankYou to our existing partners and our amazing Board Members for continuing to pull together and fight for survivors. 
•••
“You can do it on your own, but we envision a world where you don’t have to.” -SheronAnnFoundation
•••

Image may contain: text that says 'खेल-रल रत्न RAJIV खेल- GANDHI गाँधी 4 anta VNIV8 Rajiv Gandhi Khel Ratna राजीव गांधी खेल रत्न जिसे आधिकारिक तौर पर 'स्पोर्ट्स एंड गेम्स में राजीव गांधी खेल रत्न पुरस्कार' के रूप में जाना जाता है, भारत गणराज्य का सर्वोच्च खेल सम्मान है| इस पुरस्कार की शुरुआत वर्ष 1991-92 में हुई थी| यह पुरस्कार भारत सरकार के युवा एवं खेल मामलों के मंत्रालय (Ministry of Youth Affairs and Sports) द्वारा प्रतिवर्ष प्रदान किया जाता है|'.

Photo by UPSC MOTIVATIONAL on August 22, 2020. Image may contain: text that says 'Galery राजीव गांधी खेल रत्न पुरस्कार-2020 Rajiv Gandhi Khel Ratna Award Award-2020 रोहित शर्मा (क्रिकेट), मनिका बत्रा (टेबल टेनिस), विनेश फोगाट (रेसलिंग), रानी रामपाल (हॉकी), मरियप्पन थंगावेलू (पैरा-एथलीट) को वर्ष 2020 के लिये भारत के सर्वोच्च खेल सम्मान 'राजीव गांधी खेल रत्न पुरस्कार' (Rajiv Gandhi Khel Ratna Award) से सम्मानित किया जाएगा|'.

Photo by UPSC MOTIVATIONAL on August 22, 2020. Image may contain: text that says '्रमुख बिंदु: रोहित शर्मा, सचिन तेंदुलकर, एम.एस. धोनी एवं विराट कोहली के बाद चौथे ऐसे क्रिकेटर होंगे जिन्हें 'राजीव गांधी खेल रत्न पुरस्कार' से सम्मानित किया जाएगा| विनेश फोगाट अब तक एकमात्र भारतीय महिला पहलवान हैं जिन्होंने टोक्यो ओलंपिक के लिये क्वालीफाई किया था| -पूर्व पैरा-ओलंपिक पदक विजेता देवेंद्र झाझरिया और दीपा मलिक के बाद मरियप्पन थंगावेलू तीसरे भारतीय पैरा- एथलीट हैं जिन्हें राजीव गांधी खेल रत्न पुरस्कार से सम्मानित किया जाएगा| इस वर्ष COVID-19 कारण ये पुरस्कार राष्ट्रपति भवन के बजाय आभासी तरीके से राष्ट्रीय खेल दिवस के अवसर पर प्रदान किये जायेंगे|'.

node.text:
Hi, I’m Bree. 👋🏻
•
I’m a Boston girl who found my way by the Jersey shore 🌊 with my hubby and 3 year old boxer, Luna. 👩🏻‍🤝‍👨🏽🐶
•
I grew up playing soccer, basketball, softball and even football all through high school! There was no better end to my day then leaving everything on the field/court. 🏃🏻‍♀️
•
I got my PharmD from MCP in Boston, which required more time in 📚 and less time in ⚽️🏀🥎🏈. This resulted in more than your typical “freshman 15”. 🙄
•
About 1 year ago, I finally had enough and wanted my healthy lifestyle back! I joined @ww in July of 2019 and the #wwcommunity truly inspired me along the way. While working in the emergency room🚨 in the heat of #covid19 🦠may have paused my weight loss journey, I didn’t give up. WW is a lifestyle and journey, not a “diet” or destination. I hope we can help encourage each other through out our healthy journeys in this crazy world! 🌎

node.text:
-
Kampung Warna-Warni Tigarihit di Parapat menjadi destinasi wisata baru bagi wisatawan yang menikmati keindahan alam dan keramahan masyarakat sekitar Danau Toba, Sumatera Utara. 
-

Peresmiannya yang dilakukan bertepatan dengan HUT ke-75 Kemerdekaan RI merupakan momentum membangkitkan pariwisata Danau Toba yang terdampak pandemi #COVID19.
-

Beberapa pemandangan menarik yang bisa dinikmati antara lain berupa spektrum tembok warna-warni, area mural yang instagramable, pertunjukan sunset di tepi Danau Toba yang eksotis, serta parade obor dan pertunjukan lampion.
-

Menparekraf Bapak Wishnutama menyambut baik peresmian Kampung Warna-Warni Tigarihit yang menjadi daya tarik baru di Danau Toba, yang merupakan satu dari lima destinasi super prioritas yang ditetapkan pemerintah. Kampung Warna-Warni Tigarihit menjadi wujud kreativitas dan inovasi dari masyarakat dalam memaksimalkan potensi parekraf serta upaya #BangkitUntukIndonesiaMaju.
-

Garut - 

Warga Kabupaten Garut dihebohkan dengan aksi kawanan pemuda yang melucuti bendera Indonesia di pagi buta. Peristiwa tersebut kini tengah ramai diperbincangkan.

Kejadian itu berlangsung, Kamis (20/8) lalu sekira pukul 03.37 WIB di Kecamatan Wanaraja. Aksi para pemuda tersebut terekam kamera pengintai yang terpasang di lokasi.

Seperti dilihat detikcom, dalam video rekaman CCTV berdurasi 23 detik yang beredar, terlihat empat orang pemuda berjalan di trotoar.

Entah apa alasannya, para pemuda terlihat melucuti bendera Indonesia yang ada di lokasi. Dalam video rekaman CCTV itu, terlihat para pemuda mencopot dua bendera merah putih yang terpasang di sana.

Dari rekaman CCTV itu juga diketahui, empat orang pemuda tersebut terlihat menggunakan sarung. Ada yang dipakai sesuai peruntukan, ada juga yang diselendangkan.

Ciri-ciri lainnya, tiga pemuda terlihat menggunakan kopiah. Sedangkan satu pemuda lain menggunakan fedora.

"Telah terjadi pencopotan bendera merah putih tanpa sebab di Jl. Wanaraja dekat studio Albara, Garut, sekitar pukul 03.37 WIB," tulis pemilik akun dalam unggahannya.

Kejadian itu berlangsung di Jalan Raya Wanaraja, Desa Wanaraja. Tepatnya di depan studio Albara.

Polisi yang mengetahui kejadian tersebut kemudian melakukan olah tempat kejadian perkara (TKP). Berdasarkan hasil olah TKP, polisi menyebut ada empat bendera Indonesia yang dilucuti para pemuda.

"Ada empat (bendera yang diambil)," ucap Kapolsek Wanaraja Kompol Liman Heryawan kepada wartawan, Sabtu (22/8).

Liman mengatakan, saat ini pihaknya tengah mendalami kasus tersebut. Sejumlah saksi dimintai keterangannya. Selain itu polisi juga memeriksa CCTV lain yang terpasang di sekitaran lokasi kejadian.

"Kita akan dalami orang-orang yang ada di CCTV," katanya.

Sementara itu, Kabid Humas Polda Jabar Kombes Pol Erdi Caniago meminta para pemuda untuk menyerahkan diri. Erdi meminta para pelaku untuk menjelaskan maksud perbuatan itu kepada polisi.

"Prinsipnya kita sangat menyayangkan perbuatan yang dilakukan. Dengan ada kejadian tersebut, kita mengimbau untuk (menjelaskan) perbuatan tersebut kepada kepolisian Polres Garut," ucap Erdi saat dikonfirmasi detikcom via telepon, Sabtu.

node.text:
India is all set to get its first coronavirus vaccine. Covishield - the Oxford University- Astrazeneca vaccine candidate will be commercialised in 73 days, a top official at the Serum Institute of India said on Saturday.The phase III trials of the vaccine are being handled by the Serum Institute of India. The vaccine is likely to be the first one to move into production in India, sources had indicated to India Today TV earlier.A Bussiness Today report quoted a Serum Institute of India (SII) top official saying that the government has given the biotechnology company "a 'special manufacturing priority license' and fast tracked the trial protocol processes to get the trials completed in 58 days.""By this, the first dosing will take place today [Saturday] in the final phase [Phase II] and the second dosing will happen after 29 days.

Source:- india today

Image may contain: one or more people, text that says '건강들 위한 출무션 SOLUTIONS FOR EALTH 1. 입술 주위에 물집 일상생활에서 겪게 되는 가장 흔한 증상으로 '헤르페스'라고 불리는 바이러스에 의해서 생겨요. 따라서 충분한 휴식과 수면을 취하고 적절한 운동을 해 면역력을 높여야 합니다. 건강을 슬무션 SOLUTIONS FOR EALTH jünümrt 2.감기 2. 감기 면역력이 약하면 감기에 걸리기 쉽고 제때 감기가 치료되지 않고 증상이 심해지면 축농증으로 진행됩니다. 따라서 감기에 걸리지 않도록 미리 예방하거나 감기에 걸렸을때는 빨리 치료하는 것이 좋아요.'.

Photo by Yun Hui Jeon on August 22, 2020. Image may contain: 1 person, text that says '건강을 위한을무션 무酬 9SUTAE7 MCL2R4M 3.탈모 면역력의 이상이나 과도한 스트레스로 인해 부분적으로 좁은부위에 탈모가 나타나는 원형 탈모증이 생길 수 있습니다. 탈모가 의심되면 전문가의 정확한 진단을 받고 치료를 시작하는 것이 중요합니다. 건강을 위암회국원 PAUrAN 4.피부트러블 피부 트러블 면역력이 약해진 피부는 예민해져 여러가지 피부 트러블이 생기고 노화가 가속화 됩니다. 따라서, 면역력을 높여 외부 환경에 충분히 대응할 수 있는 건강한 피부를 만드는 것이 중요합니다.'.

Photo by Yun Hui Jeon on August 22, 2020. Image may contain: text that says '건강 위한술무최 위한 5. 대상포진 대상포진은 어린 시절 수두에 걸렸거나 수두 예방주사를 받은 사람에게 쉽게 나타납니다. 몸안에 남아있는 수두 바이러스가 잠복해있다가 몸의 면역력이 약해지면서 발병하는데요. 피부 발진 등이 생겨 피부질환으로 오해하곤 합니다. 건강을 위만 출공신 SOLUTAN 5. 대상포진 초기에는 감기 몸살과 증상이 비슷하지만 시간이 지나 증상이 심해지면 극심한 통증을 동반합니다.'.

Photo by Yun Hui Jeon on August 22, 2020. Image may contain: ‎one or more people, ‎text that says '‎·건강을 위한출무션 OעAD N 6. 만성피로 누적된 피로를 제때 해소해주지 않을때 면역력이 약해지기도 하지만 면역력이 약해져도 쉽게 피로감을 느껴집니다. 이때 비타민C를 충분히 섭취하면 면역력을 높이고 피로감을 멀 느낄 건강 출무션 있습니다. 7. 관절염 류마티스관절염은 자가 면역 질환으로 면역력이 저하되면 류마티스관절염 발병 확률이 높아집니다. 따라서, 일반적인 관절염 치료를 받는 것이 아니라 면역력을 정상화 시켜주는 치료 받아야 합니다.‎'‎‎.

Photo by Yun Hui Jeon on August 22, 2020. Image may contain: text that says '건강을 위만의루션 UEAL7 n 8. 질염 면역력이 떨어지면 여성은 '질염' 을 겪을 수 있습니다. 질에는 원래 균이 많아요. 질 내부를 약산성으로 유지시켜 병균에 맞설 수 있도록 하는 유익균이 대부분이어서 평소에는 招주선 8. 질염 문제가 되지 않습니다. 하지만, 몸의 면역력이 떨어지면 유익균이 감소하고 곰팡이나 트리코모나스 같은 유해균이 많아지면서 질염이 발생할 수 있어요.'.

Photo by Yun Hui Jeon on August 22, 2020. Image may contain: one or more people, text that says '김강을 위한출무션 2AU1AD4 9.배탈 배탈을 자주 겪는다면 면역력이 떨어지면 위장관으로 들어온 세균이나 바이러스를 제거하는 기능이 떨어지기 때문입니다. 또, 장내 유해균이 많아지면서 내부 염증이 생길 수 있습니다. 건강을 한솔무션 SOLUTIONS |9.배탈 배탈 따라서 음식을 먹은 후 복통이 생기고 설사를 하는 증상이 지속되면 면역력 저하를 의심해야 합니다.'.

Photo by Yun Hui Jeon on August 22, 2020. Image may contain: one or more people, text that says '222 라රപ진 வඅල AVRNP MALRL 10. 염증 '봉와직염' 이 생길 수도 있습니다. 봉와직염은 피부 아래 조직에 황색포도상구균 등의 세균이 침투해 발생하는 염증성질환입니다. 피부가 빨개지고 누르면 아프며 다리나 발에 주로 생깁니다. 건강을 위한솔무센 무센 10.염증 몸 여기저기 염증이 생긴다면. 면역력이 떨어져 각종 세균이나 바이러스가 몸에 침투하거나, 체내에 있던 것이 악화되면서 다양한 염증질환이 생길 수 있습니다.'.
Photo by Yun Hui Jeon on August 22, 2020. Image may contain: text that says '우리 몸은 최고급 외제차나, 이태리 명품백이나, 최신형 스마트폰보다 훨씬 더 오래 사용해야 합니다. 자기 자신에게 투자하세요!'.

#covid19
코로나가 다시 대유행의 조짐을 보이고있다.
남의 일이겠지 막연히 생각하고 있었건만,
.
아들이 다니는 장애인복지관 직원이 확진받고 같은시간대에 있었다 해서 가슴이 철렁.😱
다행히 동선이 겹치지 않아 검사대상에선 제외됐지만,
찝찝해서 금요일에 출근배제됨.💬
언제어디서 내가 무증상으로 감염되어 남들에게 옮기고 다닐지 모른다 생각하니 무섭다.
더구나 고위험환자들이 있는 병원에서 일하니...
출퇴근제외하곤 돌아다니면 끝이겠구나 싶음.💦
.
깜깜이 전파가 20프로 넘은 지금은,
어디서 어떻게 감염될지 알수없는일. 변종도 생기고 종식은 기대하기 어렵겠지.
언젠간 익숙해진 신종플루처럼 인류와 쭉 함게갈거란건데...
전파력이 강하니 참... 언제까지 이 몹쓸 짓을 해야할지.
.
3월때보다 지금이 더 위기고 더 철저하게 사회적 거리두기 2단계를 지켜야할 시기인것같다.
이 무더위에 헌신하는 다른 간호사샘들을 보면 저절로 반성하게됨.🙏
.
감염되더라도 중요한건 개개인의 면역력이 충분히 받쳐준다면 약하게 지나갈일.
나가지말고 무엇보다 잘자고 잘쉬고 개인위생 신경쓰고 질좋은 영양 채우면서 면역력을 키우자.💉
.
면역이란,
피부,소화관,호흡기등을 통해 침입한 세균이나 바이러스등에 대한 인체방어시스템이다.
또한 외부이물질(항원)침입시 그에 대응하는 물질(항체)를 만들어 신체를 방어하는 것.
.
면역력이 떨어졌을때 몸에 나타나는 이상신호 10가지.
대부분 아시는 증상들이겠지만 지금 우리몸은 어떤상태인지 한번 돌아보는 계기가 되길.
.

Beyond Mindfulness - Program Retreat Special  di Ubud, Bali. 

Selama pandemi ini kita mengalamai kondisi yang tidak menentu. Selama lebih dari 5 bulan terakhir ini kita dihadapkan pada kondisi yang membuat pikiran, mental, emosional kita bergejolak,  membuat kita was-was, khawatir, stress, bahkan ketakutan. 
Sekarang kondisi kita perlahan sudah mulai membaik dan semoga akan semakin membaik kedepannya. Kita sudah mulai bisa beraktifitas dengan tetap menjaga dan mengikuti protokol kesehatan. 
Dalam menghadapi kondisi seperti ini tubuh kita  membutuhkan  daya tahan tubuh yang kuat. Ketenangan pikiran, mental/emosional adalah cara alami untuk menjaga imunitas tubuh kita. 

Yoga, meditasi dan gaya hidup yang tepat dapat membantu kita meraih ketenangan dan harmoni pikiran, mental/emosional dan kesehatan tubuh kita.

node.text:
Estados de la materia.
Los estados de la materia son cuatro:
líquido, sólido, gaseoso y gato.
El gato es un estado especial de la materia,
si bien caben las dudas:
¿es materia esta voluptuosa contorsión?
¿no viene del cielo esta manera de dormir?
Y este silencio, ¿acaso no procede de un lugar sin tiempo?
Cuando el espíritu juega a ser materia
entonces se convierte en gato.
.
.

node.text:
Wuhan, China once the global epicenter of the coronavirus hosted an EDM concert at an outdoor water park that saw thousands in attendance. Wuhan hasn't had a single case of COVID-19 since mid-May.

People in Wuhan, China are now enjoying packed pool parties after three months without new locally transmitted COVID-19 cases.

Videos of joyful-looking party goers at Wuhan Maya Beach Water Park taken on August 15 were widely circulated online this week. The photos showed a crowd of people standing in a large pool and sitting in tubes at an event that featured live performances.

With no masks or social distancing in sight, the photos of so many people together mark a stark contrast to images taken earlier this year in an empty Wuhan when residents were barred from leaving their homes. The city is considered ground zero for the new coronavirus.

According to the government-run Wuhan Daily, a manager at Wuhan Maya Beach Water Park said the park currently sees an average of 15,000 people on weekends. During early August, it saw about half the number of visitors compared to the same period in previous years. Still, the sight of massive crowds closely together has struck people in parts of the world where coronavirus is still spreading.

node.text:
ไทยพบผู้ติดเชื้อโควิด-19 เพิ่ม 5 ราย จาก “อินเดีย - อังกฤษ – โอมาน”
.
วันนี้ (23 ส.ค.63) ศูนย์บริหารสถานการณ์โควิด-19 (ศบค.) รายงานสถานการณ์การแพร่ระบาดของไวรัสโควิด-19 ในประเทศว่า พบผู้ป่วยยืนยันติดเชื้อรายใหม่ 5 ราย ซึ่งเดินทางมากจากต่างประเทศ ทำให้ยอดผู้ป่วยยืนยันสะสมอยู่ที่ 3,395 ราย เป็นผู้ป่วยในประเทศ 2,444 ราย และผู้ป่วยใน State Quarantine จำนวน 458 ราย วันนี้มีผู้ป่วยรักษาหายเพิ่ม 1 ราย รวมสะสมอยู่ที่ 3,221 ราย ส่วนผู้ป่วยที่ยังรักษาตัวอยู่ในโรงพยาบาล 116 ราย ขณะที่ไม่มีผู้เสียชีวิตเพิ่ม ยอดผู้เสียชีวิตสะสมอยู่ที่ 58 ราย
.
สำหรับผู้ป่วยรายใหม่ 5 ราย ได้แก่ ผู้ที่เดินทางมาจากอินเดีย 1 ราย เป็นหญิง อายุ 41 ปี อาชีพแม่บ้าน เดินทางมาถึงไทยเมื่อวันที่ 8 ส.ค. (เที่ยวบินเดียวกับผู้ป่วยยืนยันก่อนหน้า 19 ราย) เข้าพัก State Quarantine ในกทม. และตรวจหาเชื้อครั้งที่ 3 ในวันที่ 21 ส.ค. ผลตรวจเชื้อ ให้ประวัติเคยมีอาการ (อยู่ระหว่างสอบสวน)
.
อังกฤษ 1 ราย เป็นหญิงไทย อายุ 45 ปี อาชีพรับจ้าง เดินทางถึงไทยวันที่ 10 ส.ค. เข้าพัก State Quarantine ในชลบุรี และตรวจหาเชื้อครั้งที่ 2 ในวันที่ 21 ส.ค. ผลตรวจเชื้อ ไม่มีอาการ
.
โอมาน 3 ราย เป็นหญิงไทย 2 ราย อายุ 26 ปี อาชีพว่างงาน และ 29 ปี อาชีพพนักงานโรงแรม อีก 1 ราย เป็นชายไทย อายุ 53 ปี อาชีพรับจ้าง เดินทางถึงไทยวันที่ 17 ส.ค. เข้าพัก State Quarantine ในชลบุรี และตรวจหาเชื้อครั้งที่ 1 ในวันที่ 21 ส.ค. ผลตรวจเชื้อ ทั้งหมดไม่มีอาการ
.
